{"tid":1625842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家裝修完幫手搞下海外文宣","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:24:19.000Z","uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3175d6279ef5f8bf0ecbdbbcde4396121e7636","tid":1625842,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"我識幾個都反共嘅台灣朋友，佢地問我香港示威者係咪真係暴徒化咗，冇啦啦做乜拆元氣、吉野家，我解釋翻係親中企業所以先裝修，台資企業唔會有事。<br />\n<br />\n連台仔都係咁，我諗海外更甚之。<br />\n<br />\n雖然海外力量無法直接幫拖，但國際上支持越多越好，希望手足們唔好停留係連登，多啲出其他平台(尤其英語系）幫手文宣增加前線手足嘅正當性。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"f1c26772576577ee6e9f2fe31f68d6a2e005c650","tid":1625842,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faed9bc985331f598734ec5cbbda3760b862e1f7","tid":1625842,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"外人係唔明我做緊乜的，一定話畀佢地知真相！"},{"pid":"a16002a77328dc67edb2ce0f303fd3839c68d9b9","tid":1625842,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>外人係唔明我<span style=\"color: red;\">地</span>做緊乜的，一定話畀佢地知真相！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f3d40887c8b3582f39c18abeed3c01d77d79c94d","tid":1625842,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"幫手推下"},{"pid":"754f7da1543141fc130854c7879c3e26c567e965","tid":1625842,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:42:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64ada88a95f42ee5f29d52ee347efdee898a0b85","tid":1625842,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"網絡要鍵戰"},{"pid":"0e1e5443ad9a33c562ed345f7d7cb4c294f7f9df","tid":1625842,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"60a85399423210091283d5a7560be5d497bcd941","tid":1625842,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep